reviews.review_text:
better source i saw no review on this one, so i dl'ed the other...i was unhappy w/ some crowd noise on other version, which although is still a nice listen, is distracting (check out scream as jer takes guitar break in comes a time)

i like the qual of this one more...less crowd to my ears

great sound! like always Moore does a fantastic recording, worth the dwnld. alone just for the sound, worth the listen although I only found a few songs where the boys were getting into it, kinda lackluster...I hate to say that because all these events were special and were to the ones there.
